回溯模板 <pre><code>bool Backtracking ( int i ){
    Found = false;
    if ( i &gt; N )return true; /* solved with (x1, ..., xN) */
    for ( each xi in Si ) { 
        /* check if satisfies the restriction R */
        OK = Check((x1, ..., xi) , R ); 
        /* pruning */
        if ( OK ) {
            Count xi in;
            Found = Backtracking( i+1 );
            if ( !Found )Undo( i ); 
            /* recover to (x1, ..., xi-1) */
        }
        if ( Found ) break; 
    }
    return Found;
}
</code></pre> <ul> <li>考虑对称性可以少算不少</li> </ul>
